N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7830.3 - Relationship to other rights and remedies

State Regulations

Nothing contained in this Part shall be construed to
abridge or limit any other right or remedy that a purchaser or prospective
purchaser may have at law or in equity, statutory or
otherwise. Notes
